?title=%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B7:UrlShortener&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fbn.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E0%25A6%25B8%25E0%25A6%25BE%25E0%25A6%25B9%25E0%25A6%25BE%25E0%25A6%25AF%25E0%25A7%258D%25E0%25A6%25AF%3A%25E0%25A6%25AD%25E0%25A7%2582%25E0%25A6%25AE%25E0%25A6%25BF%25E0%25A6%2595%25E0%25A6%25BE"><span>সংক্ষিপ্ত ইউআরএল নিন</span></a></li><li id="t-urlshortener-qrcode" class="mw-list-item"><a href="/w/index.php?title=%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B7:QrCode&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fbn.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E0%25A6%25B8%25E0%25A6%25BE%25E0%25A6%25B9%25E0%25A6%25BE%25E0%25A6%25AF%25E0%25A7%258D%25E0%25A6%25AF%3A%25E0%25A6%25AD%25E0%25A7%2582%25E0%25A6%25AE%25E0%25A6%25BF%25E0%25A6%2595%25E0%25A6%25BE"><span>কিউআর কোড ডাউনলোড করুন</span></a></li><li id="t-shorturl" class="mw-list-item"><a href="//bn.wikisource.org/s/89z" title="বন্টনের জন্য এই সংক্ষিপ্ত ইউআরএল অনুলিপি করুন"><span>সংক্ষিপ্ত ইউআরএল</span></a></li><li id="t-wikibase" class="mw-list-item"><a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Special:EntityPage/Q3945" title="আইটেম উপাত্ত ভান্ডারে সংযুক্ত করা লিঙ্ক [g]" accesskey="g"><span>উইকিউপাত্ত আইটেম</span></a></li>
		</ul>
		
	</div>
</div>

